title: Tsuihou Majutsushi no Sonogo: Shintenchi de Hajimeru Slow Life
altTitle: Thereafter of an Exiled Magician: Somehow My Engagement Was Cancelled, and I Was Driven Out, so I Will Stop Living the Tough Aristocrat Life, and Live Leisurely in a Distant, Foreign, Developing Village
